freetext.SYMPTOMS_DESCRIPTION: Chest pain. Presumed autoimmune flare after vaccination. Was put on steroids today, restarted plaquenil. Cardiology work Up negative.

I have reported chest pain and chest pressure since the vaccine. I thought it was GERD but it persisted. Now shortness of breath and burning chest pain over my heart. I went to PCP today and currently have Holter monitor. No dx yet.

Mild substernal chest pressure (could be GERD)
Very mild chest pressure (could be GERD)
